%% Sequence 1 — Happy path
%% Поиск → открытие меню → создание заказа → оплата → уведомление.
%% Главное: внешний API синхронный и короткий, побочные эффекты уходят в Kafka.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Клиент
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant CAT as Catalog Service
    participant OS as Order Service
    participant PS as Payment Service
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant R as Redis
    participant K as Kafka
    participant PSP as PSP (внешний)
    participant NS as Notification Service

    Note over C,GW: TLS + JWT

    C->>GW: GET /api/v1/restaurants?lat&lon&q
    GW->>CAT: forward
    CAT->>R: GET cache:search:{hash}
    R-->>CAT: miss
    CAT->>PG: SELECT (PostGIS ST_DWithin + pg_trgm)
    PG-->>CAT: 1..N ресторанов
    CAT->>R: SET cache TTL=30s
    CAT-->>GW: 200 OK
    GW-->>C: 200 OK + 32 ресторана

    C->>GW: GET /api/v1/restaurants/{id}
    GW->>CAT: forward
    CAT->>R: GET cache:menu:{id}
    R-->>CAT: hit (60% случаев)
    CAT-->>GW: 200 OK
    GW-->>C: карточка + меню

    Note over C,GW: Пользователь собирает корзину,<br/>Order Service хранит её в Redis TTL=24h

    C->>GW: POST /api/v1/orders<br/>Idempotency-Key: uuid-v7
    GW->>OS: forward
    OS->>R: GET idem:{key}
    R-->>OS: not found
    OS->>R: HGETALL cart:{user_id}
    R-->>OS: items + snapshot цен
    OS->>PG: BEGIN<br/>INSERT orders (status=awaiting_payment)<br/>INSERT outbox_events (order.created)<br/>COMMIT
    PG-->>OS: order_id
    OS->>R: SETEX idem:{key} 24h {order_id}
    OS-->>GW: 201 Created {order_id, total, awaiting_payment}
    GW-->>C: 201

    Note over PG,K: Outbox relay асинхронно<br/>публикует order.created

    C->>GW: POST /api/v1/orders/{id}/payment
    GW->>PS: forward
    PS->>PG: INSERT payments (status=processing)
    PS->>PSP: POST /intents (amount, return_url)
    PSP-->>PS: payment_intent_id, redirect_url
    PS-->>GW: 200 {redirect_url}
    GW-->>C: 302 redirect на PSP

    Note over C,PSP: Клиент подтверждает оплату<br/>(3DS / СБП)

    PSP->>GW: POST /api/v1/webhooks/psp (HMAC-signed)
    GW->>PS: forward
    PS->>PG: BEGIN<br/>SELECT ... FOR UPDATE WHERE psp_id=?<br/>UPDATE payments status=succeeded<br/>UPDATE orders status=paid<br/>INSERT outbox_events (payment.succeeded, order.paid)<br/>COMMIT
    PS-->>GW: 200 OK
    GW-->>PSP: 200 OK (идемпотентно)

    PG->>K: outbox relay → publish
    K-->>NS: consume payment.succeeded
    NS->>C: push «Заказ оплачен»
    NS->>K: commit offset
